2026-05-04

Scope:
- Only adjusted FinanceBench / financial RAG answer-generation behavior.
- Did not modify retrieval, rerank, evidence pack construction, evaluator, or frontend.

Changed files:
- backend/agent.py
- backend/tools.py

Changes:
- Tightened the finance-document system prompt to force extract-then-answer behavior.
- Instructed the model to treat search_knowledge_base output as the only allowed evidence pack.
- Required concise output with:
  - Extracted Evidence
  - If calculation is needed
  - Final Answer
- Required the model to name the specific missing field instead of giving a generic refusal.
- Required the model to avoid mismatched company/year/doc_type evidence when better-matching evidence exists.
- Reformatted search_knowledge_base tool output to label the returned context as Final Evidence Pack Used.
- Added explicit answering rules to the tool result so the model stays grounded in the provided evidence.
